data.text:
@RossettiAllen @honglinli @EricTopol I know it’s inconvenient.

What I’d really like to see is much better ventilation in buildings and carbon dioxide monitoring displayed prominently so that the actual risk can be better gauged.

It would be helpful for more than just Covid.

@RossettiAllen @honglinli @EricTopol You don’t have to eat indoors to have social contact.

And not eating indoors is not “locked down”.

And you can do it if you want. I just don’t think it’s a good idea right now.
